00:03:04.220 --> 00:03:06.699
So here's the most basic form of a GT table.

00:03:06.699 --> 00:03:12.699
It's just got column labels, a table body, pretty bog simple.

00:03:12.699 --> 00:03:14.820
But we have this other feature called a stub.

