00:03:24.899 --> 00:03:28.580
So it's not always needed, but it's actually quite useful.

00:03:28.580 --> 00:03:32.860
Now another thing you can do to add structure to a table is bundle your rows into groups,

00:03:32.860 --> 00:03:35.419
and those groups can have labels themselves.

00:03:35.419 --> 00:03:38.699
Nice way to sort of structure your data.

00:03:38.699 --> 00:03:42.580
We also let you put in a title and a subtitle in the table header.

00:03:42.580 --> 00:03:45.779
It's great for describing what the table really is.

00:03:45.779 --> 00:03:48.539
