00:03:50.339 --> 00:03:53.740
So additional information about the table.

00:03:53.740 --> 00:03:56.820
And another way to structure your data is you can structure your columns as well.

00:03:56.820 --> 00:03:58.100
Use spanners for that.

00:03:58.100 --> 00:04:01.940
We see this all the time in tables printed in, say, journals, for instance.

00:04:01.940 --> 00:04:02.940
