00:11:33.419 --> 00:11:34.419
at the values.

00:11:34.419 --> 00:11:36.760
You just look at the sort of color.

00:11:36.760 --> 00:11:38.580
And same with columns.

00:11:38.580 --> 00:11:39.580
You just look up and down.

00:11:39.580 --> 00:11:45.299
You sort of get a sense of, like, you know, what the scale is just from the colors changing.

00:11:45.299 --> 00:11:46.299
Okay.

